{"word":"G5515 - χλωρός - chlōrós - khlo-ros' - Green","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χλωρός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chlōrós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khlo-ros'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Green</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பசுமையான, மங்கின நிறமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. green"},{"paragraph":"2. yellowish, pale"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G5514 - Χλόη - Chlóē - khlo'-ay/5514\">G5514</a>; <i>greenish</i>, that is, <i>verdant</i>, <i>dun-colored:</i> - green, pale.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}